{"tid":2314004,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"太撚爛口比女友嫌棄","createTime":"2020-12-06T08:31:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-06T10:04:44.000Z","uid":375055,"like":4,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c2988c2064211f8649c47196a2a2a4ddb3b136ff","tid":2314004,"uid":375055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T08:31:57.000Z","msg":"小弟係一個地盤佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，每日唔撚講粗口唔柒舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。我每次同條女講野都加撚咗好多粗口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，佢成日屌鳩我低俗地盤佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，又唔撚同我分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。可能貪我月入50k<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n  琴日我同條女扑野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 我揸緊佢對大波波嗰陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，佢個閪窿突然收緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，搞到我碌鳩射撚咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我唔小心講咗:<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>「你個死臭閪咁好屌，唔做雞真係哂撚哂。」</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n條臭八婆嬲撚左我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，話月經到要去買m巾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，一腳伸撚左我去大西洋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,bra都未戴番就出咗門口<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,截都截唔撚住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n而家點撚算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,屌佢老母，死港女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"8345d48e0988b8b186fd5e2c997e955a9314b4ee","tid":2314004,"uid":69157,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T08:33:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K8fRPy2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK8fRPy2.jpg&h=c3044c4d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2bca0da77252e1b466780e026933f7971a94d616","tid":2314004,"uid":123696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T08:33:28.000Z","msg":"臭你又奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac9077fd4533abb6343d2083f63e7a9ae9e3f2a7","tid":2314004,"uid":118502,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T08:33:36.000Z","msg":"你quit 完u 再唔溫書 仲係日日上連登開膠po 就可能要quit 多第二次<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9209f350fe38232c17f95d701af4be138f59918b","tid":2314004,"uid":375055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac9077fd4533abb6343d2083f63e7a9ae9e3f2a7","tid":2314004,"uid":118502,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T08:33:36.000Z","msg":"你quit 完u 再唔溫書 仲係日日上連登開膠po 就可能要quit 多第二次<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T08:34:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地盤佬冇u讀"},{"pid":"91731e2b1957f8c2d6aeab80b03bfec7dc96fb8a","tid":2314004,"uid":118502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9209f350fe38232c17f95d701af4be138f59918b","tid":2314004,"uid":375055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac9077fd4533abb6343d2083f63e7a9ae9e3f2a7","tid":2314004,"uid":118502,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T08:33:36.000Z","msg":"你quit 完u 再唔溫書 仲係日日上連登開膠po 就可能要quit 多第二次<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T08:34:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地盤佬冇u讀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T08:35:42.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">好<span class=\"green\">自</span></span><span class=\"blue\">為<span class=